Southern Bell knew to the minute when 
sales by telephone opened for tickets to two Bruce Springsteen 
concerts scheduled here Their circuits promptly went on overload 
Local and longdistance calls in the Raleigh area were blocked 
temporarily after the tickets went on sale at 10 am Tuesday said 
a repair worker at Southern Bells office here 
The concerts are scheduled March 3 and 4 at the Smith Center in 
Chapel Hill 
They started this at 10 am and all of our circuits are 
overloaded because people are trying to get tickets to see him 
said the worker at Southern Bell who refused to give her name 
